('b13df8e2-47ba-4d74-a0f1-3b96f93f74a8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Traumatic exeriences of refugees. Helpful background knowledge for voluntary companionship of asylum seekers', 'In this course, it will be outlined what is meant by a psychological trauma and by which situations and psychic reactions refugees in Germany are often affected. Together, it shall be considered which support is possible in everyday life and as part of volunteer help. Also, where are the limits?\r\nThe aim of the course is to support and relieve volunteer helpers in their civil engagement through further knowledge.\r\n1x | 2 Units | feeless\r\n16H 35009\r\nDr Ilka Lennertz, psychologist', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57b76a20b6b52', 'en', '2016-09-22 16:28:56', '2016-09-22 16:28:56'),
